[
  [
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "(** * Zero objects in categories",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n    Zero objects (both initial and terminal) and zero morphisms, foundational\n    concepts for additive and stable category theory.\n*)\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "From HoTT Require Import Basics.Overture Basics.PathGroupoids Basics.Tactics.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "From HoTT.Categories Require Import Category.Core Category.Objects.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Local Open Scope morphism_scope.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** * Zero objects\n    \n    A zero object in a category is an object that is both initial and terminal.\n    Such objects play a fundamental role in additive and abelian categories,\n    where they enable the definition of zero morphisms and kernels.\n*)\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Class ZeroObject (C : PreCategory) := {\n  zero : object C;\n  is_initial :: IsInitialObject C zero;\n  is_terminal :: IsTerminalObject C zero\n}.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Coercion zero : ZeroObject >-> object.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Arguments zero {C} z : rename.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Arguments is_initial {C} z : rename.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Arguments is_terminal {C} z : rename.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Instance initialobject_zeroobject {C : PreCategory} (Z : ZeroObject C)\n  : InitialObject C\n  := {| object_initial := zero Z; isinitial_object_initial := _ |}.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Instance terminalobject_zeroobject {C : PreCategory} (Z : ZeroObject C)\n  : TerminalObject C\n  := {| object_terminal := zero Z; isterminal_object_terminal := _ |}.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** The zero morphism between any two objects is the unique morphism\n    that factors through the zero object. *)\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition zero_morphism {C : PreCategory} {Z : ZeroObject C} (X Y : object C)\n  : morphism C X Y\n  := morphism_from_initial Y o morphism_to_terminal X.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Arguments zero_morphism {C Z} X Y : simpl never.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** * Basic properties of zero objects *)\n\n(** ** Properties of zero morphisms *)\n\n(** Any morphism that factors through a zero object is the zero morphism. *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Lemma morphism_through_zero_is_zero {C : PreCategory} \n  {Z : ZeroObject C} {X Y : object C}\n  (f : morphism C X Z)\n  (g : morphism C Z Y)\n  : g o f = zero_morphism X Y.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": [
        {
          "_type": "goal",
          "name": null,
          "conclusion": "g o f = zero_morphism X Y",
          "hypotheses": [
            {
