      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Lemma zero_morphism_right {C : PreCategory} {Z : ZeroObject C}\n  {X Y W : object C}\n  (g : morphism C Y W)\n  : g o zero_morphism X Y = zero_morphism X W.",
